in game:

	if player wants to disconnect, ask if they're sure they want to disconnect
	if yes
		pause the game.  tell them that a player has disconnected and we're replacing the player with AI
		player who disconnected will send last status information to server
	
		=====
		server looks for other players who can handle the AI
		server sends disconnected player's info to player who can handle AI
		new player to handle AI will concatenate AI's info to own info and send it to server
		=== OR ===
		server launches own module for AI

	if no
		continue
